metadata.name: Blissful Serenity
metadata.description:
This is how Ai visually represents the human psyche in a calm, blissful, divine, and meditative state. An amalgamation of the following emotions; bliss, serenity, joy, peace and love. Over 33,000+ iterations for the the final piece. 

This NFT also comes with a 16 X 16 print of the piece itself, with a white barn wood frame. The physical print also comes with a smart chip embedded inside to link the physical & digital as an authentication method.
